Question: Consider the code segment below.
 Line 1: IF (a = 0)
 Line 2: {
 Line 3: b ← a + 10
 Line 4: }
 Line 5: ELSE
 Line 6: {
 Line 7: b ← a + 2O
 Line 8: }
 Which of the following changes will NOT affect the results when the code segment is executed?
Choices: A. Changing line 3 to b ← 10 B. Changing line 3 to a ← b + 10 C. Changing line 7 to b ← 20 D. Changing line 7 to a ← b + 10
Answer: A.
